<p>
  Toggle the visibility of UI elements from the <strong>View</strong> menu.
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_group_view}>Available Toggles</.help_h4>
<p>
  <strong>Toggle Conversations:</strong>
  Show or hide the left-side channel/PM tree.<br /><strong>Toggle Nicklist:</strong>
  Show or hide the right-side user list.
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_link}>See Also</.help_h4>
<p>
  <.help_link topic="keyboard-shortcuts">Keyboard Shortcuts</.help_link>
</p>
